Achievements.Name: Basic Training
Achievements.Description: Complete the basic training in the beginning of Saint Lo.

Achievements.Name: American Infantryman
Achievements.Description: Complete two missions as an American soldier.

Achievements.Name: British Commando
Achievements.Description: Complete two missions as a British soldier.

Achievements.Name: Canadian Highlander
Achievements.Description: Complete two missions as a Canadian soldier.

Achievements.Name: Polish Tanker
Achievements.Description: Complete two missions as a Polish soldier.

Achievements.Name: Won the War
Achievements.Description: Complete the single player campaign on any difficulty setting.

Achievements.Name: Hot Potato
Achievements.Description: Pick up and return 5 live grenades.

Achievements.Name: Rifleman
Achievements.Description: Complete a mission by firing only bolt action rifles.  Melee attacks don't count.

Achievements.Name: Assault Trooper
Achievements.Description: Complete a mission by firing only assault rifles. Melee attacks don't count.

Achievements.Name: Battlefield Scavenger
Achievements.Description: Complete a mission by firing only German weapons.  Melee attacks don't count.

Achievements.Name: Still Ticking
Achievements.Description: Complete a mission without dying or using checkpoints.

Achievements.Name: Allergic to Bullets
Achievements.Description: Avoid getting hit more than 30 times during a mission.

Achievements.Name: Conservationist
Achievements.Description: Complete a mission using less than 300 rounds of ammunition.

Achievements.Name: Close Quarter Combatant
Achievements.Description: Complete a mission without firing a round. Player can make use of melee attacks and hand grenades.

Achievements.Name: Grizzled Veteran
Achievements.Description: Complete the Single Player Campaign on Veteran difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Supply Officer
Achievements.Description:
Supply ammunition to at least 20 friendly soldiers in a single ranked match.
(Multiplayer)

Achievements.Name: Doc
Achievements.Description:
Revive 10 of your teammates in a ranked match without getting a teamkill.
(Multiplayer)

Achievements.Name: A War Hero
Achievements.Description:
Capture the final objective in the game mode War. Must be a ranked match.
(Multiplayer)

Achievements.Name: Victory Medal
Achievements.Description:
Be the player with the highest score and on the winning team in a ranked match.
(Multiplayer)

Achievements.Name: Lieutenant
Achievements.Description:
Receive 200 total points in ranked matches.
(Multiplayer)

Achievements.Name: Captain
Achievements.Description:
Receive 2000 total points in ranked matches.
(Multiplayer)

Achievements.Name: Major
Achievements.Description:
Receive 8000 total points in ranked matches.
(Multiplayer)

Achievements.Name: Colonel
Achievements.Description:
Receive 20000 total points in ranked matches.
(Multiplayer)

Achievements.Name: General
Achievements.Description:
Receive 40000 total points in ranked matches.
(Multiplayer)

Achievements.Name: Purple Heart
Achievements.Description: For perserverence despite grevious injuries.

Achievements.Name: Big Air
Achievements.Description: EXTREME! Found a big jump and caught some air!
